        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="_FUVzvGfVmQXasiZJaL7-5" value="&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;[...] Organic farming in&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;particular holds great potential for farmers and consumers alike. The sector creates jobs&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;and attracts young farmers. Organic farming also&amp;nbsp; provides 10-20 % more jobs per hectare&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;than conventional farms, and creates&amp;nbsp; added value for agricultural products32. To make the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;most of this potential, at least 25% of the EU’s agricultural land must be organically&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;farmed by 2030. [...]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;Soil is a hugely&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;important non-renewable resource, vital for human and economic health, as well as the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;production of food and new medications.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;https://eur-lex.europa.eu/resource.html?uri=cellar:a3c806a6-9ab3-11ea-9d2d-01aa75ed71a1.0001.02/DOC_1&amp;amp;format=PDF&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Architects Daughter;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DArchitects%2BDaughter;strokeWidth=3;fontSize=19;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="419" y="-780" width="613" height="347" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="_FUVzvGfVmQXasiZJaL7-19" value="&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;EXPLORATORIES &lt;br&gt;STAKEHOLDER SURVEY&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;Should be used with care: Survey asks for prioritization at the final level (sensu cascade mdoel) and for the whole lanndscape, while for soils many services measured are at the regulating/supporting level or at the local and plot scale!&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="ellipse;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Architects Daughter;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DArchitects%2BDaughter;" parent="1" vertex="1">
