        <mxCell id="qbSbhaLCdoeS2R9ko5mn-3" value="&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(240, 10, 40); font-family: Verdana; font-size: 21px; text-align: left; background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;AMYNTAS ET AL: 2024:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana; font-size: 21px; text-align: left; background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ffffff&quot;&gt;Herbivory slightly increased with species richness BUT at the same time productivity also increased resulting in increased root biomass. Predation of herbivores also slightly increased. Therefore net herbivore pressure on plants decreased with increasing plant species richness.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Architects Daughter;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DArchitects%2BDaughter;strokeWidth=3;fontSize=19;" parent="1" vertex="1">
